<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="es">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="../public/chat.css">
    <title>AI Assistant</title>
   
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <!-- Barra lateral -->
        <div class="sidebar">
            <div class="logo">AI Assistant</div>
            
            <button class="new-chat-btn" onclick="newChat()">
                ‚ú® Nuevo Chat
            </button>
            
            <div class="chat-history">
                <div class="history-title">Historial</div>
                <div id="chatHistory">
                    <div class="chat-item active">
                        <div class="chat-title">Conversaci√≥n General</div>
                        <div class="chat-preview">¬øC√≥mo puedo ayudarte hoy?</div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="chat-item">
                        <div class="chat-title">Programaci√≥n Web</div>
                        <div class="chat-preview">Ayuda con HTML y CSS...</div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="chat-item">
                        <div class="chat-title">Recetas de Cocina</div>
                        <div class="chat-preview">Ideas para cenas saludables...</div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="chat-item">
                        <div class="chat-title">Consejos de Estudio</div>
                        <div class="chat-preview">T√©cnicas de memorizaci√≥n...</div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- √Årea principal del chat -->
        <div class="chat-area">
            <div class="chat-header">
                <div class="chat-title-main">Chat con IA</div>
                <div class="chat-subtitle">Tu asistente inteligente est√° listo para ayudarte</div>
            </div>

            <div class="chat-messages" id="chatMessages">
                <div class="message ai">
                    ¬°Hola! üëã Soy tu asistente de IA. ¬øEn qu√© puedo ayudarte hoy? Puedo responder preguntas, ayudarte con tareas, generar contenido creativo y mucho m√°s.
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="chat-input-area">
                <div class="input-container">
                    <textarea 
                        class="chat-input" 
                        id="messageInput"
                        placeholder="Escribe tu mensaje aqu√≠..." 
                        rows="1"
                        onkeypress="handleKeyPress(event)"
                    ></textarea>
                    <button class="send-btn" onclick="sendMessage()">
                        Enviar üöÄ
                    </button>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
<script src="https://code.jquery.com/jquery-3.7.1.min.js"></script>
<script src="/javascript/chat.js"></script>

    <!-- Scripts quitalo si queres -->
     <script>
        $(document).ready(function(){
            // Al hacer clic en la etiqueta p con id "toggle-fuentes"
            $(document).on('click', '#toggle-fuentes', function() {
               
                // Alternar la visibilidad del div con id "fuentes-contenido"
                $('#fuentes-contenido').slideToggle(); // Puedes usar .toggle() o .fadeToggle() tambi√©n
            });
        });
    </script>

    <style>
        #fuentes-contenido {
            display: none; /* Inicialmente oculto */
            border: 1px solid #ccc;
            padding: 10px;
            margin-top: 10px;
            background-color: #f9f9f9;
        }
        #toggle-fuentes {
            cursor: pointer; /* Cambia el cursor para indicar que es clickeable */
            color: blue;
            text-decoration: underline;
        }
         .sources-outside {
            display: flex;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
            gap: 8px;
            margin: 8px 0 18px 12px; /* margen izquierdo m√°s peque√±o para mayor alineaci√≥n */
            background: none;
            border: none;
            box-shadow: none;
            padding: 0;
            max-width: 90%;
        }

        .sources-outside strong {
            display: none;
        }

        .sources-outside ul {
            display: flex;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
            gap: 8px;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            list-style: none;
        }

        .sources-outside li {
            background: #eaf1fb; /* Color de fondo similar al chat de la IA */
            border: 1px solid #d0e2fa;
            border-radius: 7px;
            box-shadow: none;
            padding: 4px 10px 4px 8px;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            font-size: 0.88em;
            transition: box-shadow 0.2s, border 0.2s;
            min-width: 0;
        }

        .sources-outside li:hover {
            border: 1.5px solid #007bff;
            background: #d6e8fc;
        }

        .sources-outside a {
            color: #007bff;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-weight: 500;
            margin-left: 4px;
            transition: color 0.2s;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 2px;
            font-size: 0.95em;
        }

        .sources-outside a:hover {
            color: #0056b3;
            text-decoration: underline;
        }

        .sources-outside li::before {
            content: "üîó";
            font-size: 0.95em;
            margin-right: 3px;
            opacity: 0.7;
        }
    </style>

    

    <style>
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }

        body {
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%);
            height: 100vh;
            overflow: hidden;
        }

        .container {
            display: flex;
            height: 100vh;
            backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
        }

        /* Barra lateral */
        .sidebar {
            width: 300px;
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
            backdrop-filter: blur(20px);
            border-right: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.2);
            padding: 20px;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
        }

        .sidebar:hover {
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.15);
        }

        .logo {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
            color: white;
            font-size: 24px;
            font-weight: bold;
        }

        .logo::before {
            content: "ü§ñ";
            margin-right: 10px;
            font-size: 28px;
        }

        .new-chat-btn {
            background: linear-gradient(45deg, #ff6b6b, #ffa726);
            color: white;
            border: none;
            padding: 15px 20px;
            border-radius: 15px;
            font-size: 16px;
            font-weight: 600;
            cursor: pointer;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(255, 107, 107, 0.3);
        }

        .new-chat-btn:hover {
            transform: translateY(-2px);
            box-shadow: 0 6px 20px rgba(255, 107, 107, 0.4);
        }

        .chat-history {
            flex: 1;
            overflow-y: auto;
        }

        .history-title {
            color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.8);
            font-size: 14px;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 1px;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
            font-weight: 600;
        }

        .chat-item {
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
            border-radius: 10px;
            padding: 12px 15px;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
            color: white;
            cursor: pointer;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
            border: 1px solid transparent;
        }

        .chat-item:hover {
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.2);
            border-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.3);
            transform: translateX(5px);
        }

        .chat-item.active {
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.25);
            border-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.4);
        }

        .chat-title {
            font-weight: 600;
            margin-bottom: 5px;
            font-size: 14px;
        }

        .chat-preview {
            font-size: 12px;
            opacity: 0.7;
            white-space: nowrap;
            overflow: hidden;
            text-overflow: ellipsis;
        }

        /* √Årea principal del chat */
        .chat-area {
            flex: 1;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05);
        }

        .chat-header {
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
            padding: 20px 30px;
            border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
            color: white;
        }

        .chat-title-main {
            font-size: 20px;
            font-weight: 600;
            margin-bottom: 5px;
        }

        .chat-subtitle {
            opacity: 0.7;
            font-size: 14px;
        }

        .chat-messages {
            flex: 1;
            padding: 30px;
            overflow-y: auto;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            gap: 20px;
        }

        .message {
            max-width: 80%;
            padding: 15px 20px;
            border-radius: 20px;
            animation: fadeInUp 0.3s ease;
        }

        .message.user {
            background: linear-gradient(45deg, #667eea, #764ba2);
            color: white;
            align-self: flex-end;
            border-bottom-right-radius: 5px;
        }

        .message.ai {
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.15);
            color: white;
            align-self: flex-start;
            border-bottom-left-radius: 5px;
            backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
        }

        .chat-input-area {
            padding: 20px 30px;
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
            border-top: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
        }

        .input-container {
            display: flex;
            gap: 15px;
            align-items: end;
        }

        .chat-input {
            flex: 1;
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.15);
            border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.2);
            border-radius: 15px;
            padding: 15px 20px;
            color: white;
            font-size: 16px;
            resize: none;
            outline: none;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
            backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
        }

        .chat-input::placeholder {
            color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.6);
        }

        .chat-input:focus {
            border-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.4);
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.2);
        }

        .send-btn {
            background: linear-gradient(45deg, #667eea, #764ba2);
            border: none;
            border-radius: 12px;
            padding: 15px 20px;
            color: white;
            cursor: pointer;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
            font-size: 16px;
            font-weight: 600;
        }

        .send-btn:hover {
            transform: translateY(-2px);
            box-shadow: 0 6px 20px rgba(102, 126, 234, 0.4);
        }

        @keyframes fadeInUp {
            from {
                opacity: 0;
                transform: translateY(20px);
            }
            to {
                opacity: 1;
                transform: translateY(0);
            }
        }

        /* Scrollbar personalizada */
        ::-webkit-scrollbar {
            width: 6px;
        }

        ::-webkit-scrollbar-track {
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
            border-radius: 3px;
        }

        ::-webkit-scrollbar-thumb {
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.3);
            border-radius: 3px;
        }

        ::-webkit-scrollbar-thumb:hover {
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.5);
        }

        /* Responsive */
        @media (max-width: 768px) {
            .sidebar {
                width: 250px;
            }
            
            .chat-messages {
                padding: 20px;
            }
            
            .message {
                max-width: 90%;
            }
        }
    </style>
</body>
</html>